The timing of the model is as follows. At time 0, all shares are held by the uninformed. At time 1, the informed party (either a truthful party or a manipulator) can enter the market. The informed party is the manipulator with probability γ, and the informed party is truthful with probability δ.8Since, by definition, the informed party will be truthful only if the future stock value is high (
